en-us: Health care, public safety, and critical COVID-19 infrastructure personnel should contact their employer or their professional associations to learn how to get a vaccine.
This includes patient- or public-facing health care, long-term care, and public safety personnel

The federal government as identified workers at pre-primary, primary, and secondary schools, Head Start and Early Head Start programs, including teachers, staff, and bus drivers and those who work as or for licensed child care providers, including center-based and family care providers as now eligible for vaccination.
